<h3>Step 2: write a wiki engine</h3>
<img src="images/engine.jpg" style="float: left; margin-right: 30px">
<p>
The result was <a
href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/CGI-Wiki/">CGI::Wiki</a>.
</p>
<ul>
  <li>a toolkit for building wiki applications from</li>
  <li>database-agnostic, choice of formatters (or write your own), version control, yada yada yada</li>
  <li>extensible with plugins</li>
</ul>
<p>
Then we layered the features we needed on top to produce a stand-alone
application.
</p>